message: Add a simple features.xml and setup instructions.
Add more details and fix NPE.
Playback state changes on the graph.
Move the JAXB model out to another module and extend the XSD to support alarm and incident definitions.
Get stuff to load in Karaf again.
Send events over Kafka to OpenNMS instead of via REST.

OCE-4: 1+K Active/Standby redundancy (#28)

* 1+K Active/Standby redundancy for OCE

* Minor refactor of the expiring map

* Minor refactor of the ActiveStandbySituationProcessor

* Implemented review feedback

* Implemented more review feedback

OCE-16: Migration 'incident' to 'situation' throughout the codebase (#34)

* OCE-16: Initial migration 'incident' to 'situation'

* OCE-16: correct overzealous name conversion

* OCE-16: address merge conflicts
Update more references to use Kafka.

Add RPM packages and include an installation guide.
